item.title: My First Blog.
item.description: Brennan, a 5th year Computer Science student, called me a “Zoomer” when I made a joke about him being old. I did not know what it meant and I bet a lot of people do not know either. So, after extensive research, I decided to educate my readers on the term “Zoomer”. Zoomer It is a term use to mock members of Generation Z (people born mid-1990s to early-2000s) and is a play off the word “Boomer.
